>From the Editor:
****************
If your New Year's resolutions involve battling evil and emptying your clip
into advancing hordes of the undead, then we can help! First, some advice:
get some help, and get it now. Second, pre-order your copies of Resident
Evil 2 and Resident Evil 3 for GameCube!

The second and third chapters of the celebrated survival horror series,
which now calls GameCube its official home, benefit from the graphic
enhancements of Nintendo's 'Cube with diluting the terror and the thrills.
Just follow these links to add RE2 and RE3 to your GameCube library:

Resident Evil 2
http://www.ebgames.com/ebx/nl.asp?pf_id=222511&site=NLF0107

Resident Evil 3: Nemesis
http://www.ebgames.com/ebx/nl.asp?pf_id=226561&site=NLF0107

Then read on for this week's newsletter special and hot upcoming titles,
including Command & Conquer: Generals for PC, The Getaway and The Sims for
PS2 and a Metal Gear Solid 2 for Xbox deal that you can't refuse.


