Pre-order C&C: Generals and get a free Officer's Club Kit

The latest Command & Conquer game for PC ships in about a month, so now is
the time to place your pre-order and reserve your copy of the Officer's Club
Kit, which includes a bonus CD, a multiplayer map strategies card and a
four-color tech tree card. All of these come in handy when you've got GLA
guerillas in the wire. And the game? Full-on C&C warfare, blazing 3D
graphics and battlefield experience that adds up to improved unit
effectiveness, new units and more. Just follow this link to pre-order today:

http://www.ebgames.com/ebx/nl.asp?pf_id=218947&site=NLF0107


