>3>>
*****
The Getaway for PS2

Play a retired bank robber unwillingly pulled back into the gangster
business in Sony's PS2 thriller, The Getaway. Set in London, The Getaway
boasts a cinematic attention to detail and setting; driving sequences occur
in a virtual London recreated street by street. Add to that a British
gangster story line, heated shootouts, breathtaking graphics and a long list
of gameplay innovations. The Getaway ships in two weeks, so pre-order now:

http://www.ebgames.com/ebx/nl.asp?pf_id=224317&site=NLF0107


