>4>>
*****
The Sims for PlayStation 2

The best-selling PC game of all time is set to make its console debut on the
PS2. In addition to all the toilet cleaning, meal preparation and nap time
that you can handle, the PS2 version adds level-based gameplay and a new 3D
world. Get a friend to join in with two-player gameplay. Save your house and
Sims on a memory card and play them on a friend's system. The Sims for PS2
ships next week, so follow this link to pre-order now:

http://www.ebgames.com/ebx/nl.asp?pf_id=226058&site=NLF0107


